{{Infobox gotra
| name = Haikhani
| type = Punjabi Tribe
| location = [[Punjab (Pakistan)]]
| religion = [[Islam]]
| language = [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]]
}}
'''Haikhani''' is the name of a small [[Punjabi people|Punjabi]] [[Muslim]] tribe originating principally in [[Punjab, Pakistan|West Punjab]], originally concentrated in some parts of [[Lahore]].

In accordance to their traditions, the Haikhani are descended from [[Ghaznavids|Ghaznavid]] [[Pashtuns|Pashtun]]s.

[[Category:Punjabi tribes]]
[[Category:Social groups of Pakistan]]


